POST {{hostName}}/update-branch-password/303
Authorization: Bearer {{gsmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "password": "newpassword"
}

### Delete Branch User
POST {{hostName}}/delete-branch-users/303
Authorization: Bearer {{gsmToken}}

### Get Branch Users by Zonal
GET {{hostName}}/get-branch-users-by-zonal/201
Authorization: Bearer {{gsmToken}}

# ==========================================
# USER MANAGEMENT - Zonal
# ==========================================

### Create Zonal User
POST {{hostName}}/create-zonal-users
Authorization: Bearer {{gsmToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

